sentences: Chris Minh Doky (born 7 February 1969) is a Vietnamese-Danish jazz bassist.
He released his first album, Appreciation, in 1989 four years after picking up the instrument.
His wife Tanja is a lady-in-waiting to Denmark's Crown Princess Mary.
The Toronto Concert (Maracatu, 1992) with Niels Lan Doky, John Abercrombie, Adam Nussbaum
